    <h3 id="LowlandExpertise">
        <image src="images/JW/Lowland_Expertise.png" alt="lowland expertise icon" style="width:40px;"/>Lowland Expertise
    </h3>
    
    <p>
        Lowland Expertise is a buff you can purchase from each of the <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/B3DEEC72BBEF0C6FC6FEF835A0E275FCB1151BB7/102439.png" alt="heart" style="width:20px;"/>hearts in Janthir Wilds.
        This buff is per character, so you'll need to do this for each character you plan to Converge with.
        Each stack of Lowland Expertise gives a different buff:
    </p>
    <ol>
        <li>+10%  <image src="/icons/15px-Experience.png" alt="exp" style="width:15px;" /> Experience</li>
        <li>+10% <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/94953FA23D3E0D23559624015DFEA4CFAA07F0E5/155026.png" alt="karma" style="width:20px;"/> Karma </li>
        <li>+10% <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/98457F504BA2FAC8457F532C4B30EDC23929ACF9/619316.png" alt="gold" style="width:20px;"/> Gold </li>
        <li>Gain additional map material from Kodan Caches</li>
        <li>Gain <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/96D90DF84CAFE008233DD1C2606A12C1A0E68048/102842.png" alt="fury icon" style="width:20px;"/>fury when striking an enemy with the warclaw's dismount attack</li>
        <li>Gain additional <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/662D371A6C145EDDDA2DE6B53BC05F5F08CE386F/2596977.png" alt="unusual coins" style="width:20px;"/>Unusual Coins from Kodan Caches</li>
        <li>+5% Damage vs. titanspawn</li>
    </ol>
    <p>
        As far as Convergences go, we care only about the 5th and 7th stacks.
    </p>
    <p>
        You can farm all 7 stacks in a single day. Each of the <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/B3DEEC72BBEF0C6FC6FEF835A0E275FCB1151BB7/102439.png" alt="heart" style="width:20px;"/>hearts in Janthir Wilds sells it after completing that <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/B3DEEC72BBEF0C6FC6FEF835A0E275FCB1151BB7/102439.png" alt="heart" style="width:20px;"/>heart.
    </p>
    <p>
        Each time you buy <image src="images/JW/Lowland_Expertise.png" alt="lowland expertise icon" style="width:20px;"/>Lowland Expertise, it adds a stack. Additional purchases won't increase it past 7 stacks, but will increase the timer before it expires by 4 hours. This timer also caps at 24 hours.
        You should only need to do some <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/B3DEEC72BBEF0C6FC6FEF835A0E275FCB1151BB7/102439.png" alt="heart" style="width:20px;"/>hearts every couple days to keep the buff up, as it doesn't count down unless you're logged in on that character. 
    </p>
    <p class="caution">If you let it expire, you will need to redo all 7 stacks of <image src="images/JW/Lowland_Expertise.png" alt="lowland expertise icon" style="width:20px;"/>Lowland Expertise.</p>
